---
import StandaloneLayout from '../layouts/StandaloneLayout.astro';
---

<StandaloneLayout title="Authors" description="Internal author documentation — not linked from the public STEMSketch site.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <h1 class="section__title">Author STEM knowledge packs</h1>
      <p class="section__lead">
        Architecture F unifies ontology, ops, semantic figures, views, layouts, and catalog templates in one signed pack — the handoff contract to the end-user editor.
      </p>

      <h2 class="section__title" style="font-size: 1.35rem; margin-top: 2.5rem">Architecture F layers</h2>
      <p class="section__lead">Authors work top-down through validated layers. End-users never see L1–L2 artifacts — they consume L3 templates as catalog entries.</p>
      <div class="grid-2">
        <article class="card"><h3>L1 — Reality</h3><p>Ontology, ops, golden tests, optional KerML/SysML model transpile.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>L2 — Projection</h3><p>Semantic figures, view bindings, and layouts project graph state into presentation scenes.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>L3 — Scenarios</h3><p>Catalog templates with ScenarioSpec blocks — parameter metadata for end-user forms.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>L4 — Composition</h3><p>ViewDecks, slides, and timing — end-user only.</p></article>
      </div>

      <h2 class="section__title" style="font-size: 1.35rem; margin-top: 2.5rem">Author toolchain</h2>
      <ul class="doc-list" style="margin-top: 1rem">
        <li><a href="https://github.com/stemsketch/app/tree/main/extensions/stemsketch-knowledge" rel="noopener noreferrer">VS Code extension</a><span>Validate, golden tests, preview, sign bundles</span></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/stemsketch/author-studio" rel="noopener noreferrer">author-studio</a><span>Preconfigured author workspace</span></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/stemsketch/author-services" rel="noopener noreferrer">author-services</a><span>HTTP API for enterprise edition</span></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/stemsketch/app/blob/main/docs/architecture.md" rel="noopener noreferrer">Architecture doc</a><span>Platform monorepo reference</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</StandaloneLayout>

<style>
  .doc-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .doc-list li {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .doc-list a {
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .doc-list span {
    display: block;
    color: var(--ss-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-top: 0.2rem;
  }
</style>
